  Welcome to Week 3

Welcome to Week 3!

This week is all about cinematography. While in the last few weeks we took a look at using Midjourney to prompt and generate static shots. This week, we're going to take a deeper look into adding movement to your shots.

We'll also take a look at how we can use Generative Fill to art-direct and assist with the Cinematography and VFX process. This week will be more technical than the last two weeks, but I promise to guide you every step of the way.

By the end of this week, my hope is that you will know how to create cinematic shots using AI-produced imagery.
